oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Vegetables on display at "Horticulture, Vegetables and Truck" as part of the Tennessee Home Food Supply Program.
The Home Food Supply Program was started as a response to economic conditions by Gov. Prentice Cooper. The program aimed to help Tennesseans learn how to grow food for self-sustaining purposes.
